  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kdeartwork</title>

    <para><application>Kdeartwork</application> provides additional
    <application>KDE</application> themes, screensavers, sounds, wallpapers,
    widget styles, and window styles.</para>

    &lfs70_checked;

